Yes. sir.

18
00:05:18.485 --> 00:05:19.854
Ready to fire.

19
00:05:20.655 --> 00:05:21.656
Let it fly!

20
00:05:31.199 --> 00:05:33.000
Yeah! Hell of a shot. B!

21
